 <p style=3D'margin:0in;margin-left:.75in;line-height:18pt;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
 font-size:14.0pt;color:#244061'>&nbsp;</p>
 <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
  margin-bottom:0in'>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:#244061'><span
      style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:16.0pt'>心肌症定義：</span></li>
  <ul type=3Dcircle style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
   margin-bottom:0in'>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;line-height:
       18pt'><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:14.0pt'>心肌症是指心臟肌肉或功能異常的疾病，且排除由其他結構性心臟疾病引起的心臟功能障礙，如冠狀動脈病、原發性瓣膜病或重度高血壓。</span></li>
  </ul>
 </ul>
 <p style=3D'margin:0in;line-height:18pt;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
 font-size:11.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>
 <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
  margin-bottom:0in'>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:black'><span
      style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:16.0pt;color:#244061'>分類：</span></li>
  <ul type=3Dcircle style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
   margin-bottom:0in'>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;line-height:
       18pt'><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:14.0pt'>基於解剖學標本和超音波的發現，分為</span><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:14.0pt;color:#C00000'>擴張型、限制型</span><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:14.0pt'>和</span><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:14.0pt;color:#C00000'>肥厚型</span><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:14.0pt'>三類。</span></li>
  </ul>
 </ul>
 <p style=3D'margin:0in;margin-left:.375in;line-height:18pt;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
 font-size:14.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>
 <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
  margin-bottom:0in'>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:black'><span
      style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:16.0pt;color:#244061'>擴大型心肌症
      Dilated cardiomyopathy， DCM </span></li>
  <ul type=3Dcircle style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
   margin-bottom:0in'>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:black'><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:14.0pt;color:#244061'>定義：</span></li>
   <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
    margin-bottom:0in'>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
        style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>心壁變薄，主要特徵為</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000'>左心室擴大</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>與</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000'>收縮功能下降</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>（左心室射出分數降低
        HFrEF(&lt;40%)），收縮功能不全比舒張功能障礙更為明顯。</span></li>
   </ul>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:black'><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:14.0pt;color:#244061'>病生理：
       </span></li>
   <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
    margin-bottom:0in'>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
        style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>初期部分心肌細胞壞死，部分細胞進入細胞凋亡（apoptosis）</span></li>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
        style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>剩餘心肌細胞因壁應力增加而代償性肥大</span></li>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
        style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>間質重塑影響舒張功能，導致進一步心室擴大</span></li>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
        style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>二尖瓣逆流（MR）因瓣膜裝置受拉扯變形，加劇心衰竭</span></li>
   </ul>
   <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
    margin-bottom:0in'>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:black'><span
        style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;color:black'>右心室受影響（常因繼發性肺高壓或左心室機械交互作用）</span></li>
   </ul>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:black'><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:14.0pt;color:#244061'>主要病因分類：
       </span></li>
   <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
    margin-bottom:0in'>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:black'><span
        style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000'>Congenital/Genetic（遺傳性）
        </span></li>
    <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
     margin-bottom:0in'>
     <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
         style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>家族性 DCM </span></li>
     <ul type=3Dcircle style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
      margin-bottom:0in'>
      <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
          style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>遺傳基因與家族影響 </span></li>
      <ul type=3Dsquare style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
       margin-bottom:0in'>
       <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
           style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>DCM
           的家族遺傳率超過 30%。</span></li>
      </ul>
      <ul type=3Dsquare style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
       margin-bottom:0in'>
       <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;
           color:black'><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
           font-size:11.0pt;color:black'>最常見的基因突變為</span><span
           style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000'>
           TTN（Titin），</span><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
           font-size:11.0pt;color:black'>占家族性 DCM 的 25%，男性通常比女性早 10 年發病。</span></li>
       <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;
           color:black'><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
           font-size:11.0pt;color:black'>粗細肌絲相關基因（如 </span><span
           style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000'>MYH7、ACTC1</span><span
           style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;color:black'>）突變約占
           8%，可能在兒童期發病。</span></li>
      </ul>
      <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
          style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>特定基因變異與臨床表現
          </span></li>
      <ul type=3Dsquare style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
       margin-bottom:0in'>
       <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
           style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>致心律失常性心肌病（Arrhythmogenic
           Cardiomyopathy）： </span></li>
       <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
        margin-bottom:0in'>
        <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
            style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>由橋粒蛋白（desmosomal
            proteins）突變導致。</span></li>
        <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
            style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>影響右心室（ARVC）或雙心室，早期症狀多為
            心室心律不整（VT），可進展至心臟衰竭。</span></li>
        <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
            style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>影像學顯示心肌被脂肪組織取代，MRI
            更能清楚顯示右心室壁變薄。</span></li>
       </ul>
       <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
           style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>核膜蛋白（Lamin
           A/C）突變（約 5%）：常見於心律不整、傳導異常先於心肌病變發生的患者。</span></li>
      </ul>
     </ul>
    </ul>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:black'><span
        style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000'>Acquired（後天獲得性）
        </span></li>
    <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
     margin-bottom:0in'>
     <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:black'><span
         style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>病毒性心肌炎（腺病毒、柯薩奇病毒
         B）</span></li>
     <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:black'><span
         style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>營養缺乏（腳氣病
         BeriBeri —維生素 B1 缺乏）</span></li>
     <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:black'><span
         style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>章魚壺心肌症，由生理或情緒壓力引起之短暫性心肌病變</span></li>
    </ul>
   </ul>
   <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
    margin-bottom:0in'>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:black'><span
        style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000'>Volume/Pressure
        Overload（負荷過重） </span></li>
    <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
     margin-bottom:0in'>
     <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:black'><span
         style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>長期高血壓</span></li>
     <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:black'><span
         style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>瓣膜性心臟病（如重度主動脈瓣或二尖瓣逆流）</span></li>
    </ul>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:black'><span
        style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000'>Toxic/Metabolic（毒性/代謝性）
        </span></li>
    <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
     margin-bottom:0in'>
     <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:black'><span
         style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>內分泌疾病（甲狀腺功能異常、糖尿病）</span></li>
     <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:black'><span
         style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>溶小體儲積症</span></li>
     <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:black'><span
         style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>鐵沉積症（血色素沉著症）</span></li>
     <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:black'><span
