    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
        style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>早期症狀為運動耐受度下降，但常被忽略，直到出現充血性心衰竭症狀才被診斷</span></li>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
        style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>RCM
